tourBios.otherCarHigh: Finished 13th at the 2015 Mainland China Qualifying Tournament in early March at Wolong Lake GC in Liuzhou to secure fully-exempt playing privileges for the season...Played in four 2014 PGA TOUR China Series' events, making the cut at the United Investment Real Estate Wuhan Open (T57) and the Mission Hills Haikou Open (T62)…Made his third consecutive start to begin his season but made his appearance at the United Investment Real Estate Wuhan Open his best yet as he picked up his first top-10 of his career—a T5 at Wuhan Yishan GC. Shot rounds of 68-70 on the weekend to tie with T.K. Kim, Daniel Pearce and Alex Hawley while picking up low-amateur honors.

dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the PGA Tour China Serie was T5th in 2015 at the United Investment Real Estate Wuhan Open.
dyn.dynStats: He ranks 84th in Scoring Average (Actual) on the PGA Tour China Series.
